[02:16.58]The day of my departure at length arrived. 
我起程的日子终于来到了.

[02:20.53]Clerval spent the last evening with us.   He had endeavoured to persuade his father to permit him to accompany me and to become my fellow student, but in vain.   His father was a narrow-minded（心胸狭窄的） trader and saw idleness and ruin in the aspirations and ambition of his son. 
