[03:24.96]I threw myself into the chaise that was to convey me away and indulged in the most melancholy reflections. 
我钻进即将载我远行的马车，心头泛起最伤感的情怀。

[03:32.78]I, who had ever been surrounded by amiable companions, continually engaged in endeavouring to bestow mutual pleasure-I was now alone.   In the university whither（何处，哪里） I was going I must form my own friends and be my own protector. 
